description:
Late Nite Chef Fight - Season 1, Episode 7




Should I Stay or Escargot?

Laila Ali and Vic "Vegas" Moea pit two of Sin City's top 5-star chefs in a food truck battle to end them all. With the chance to get first pick of a food truck, the knives come out in a night of saucy French surprises. Spike Mendelsohn and Chris Oh judge.




Original Air Date: 10-Jan-2015
